# Design System

Read `docs/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md` for full tokens. Apply on every UI screen.

## Colors
- Primary olive: `#49630b`, `#5b7a12`, `#68852a`, `#8fb837`
- Soft green bg: `#f0f5e4`
- Page bg: `#f3f4f6` (gray-100); cards: white
- Neutrals: `#000`, `#fff`, gray scale through `#4b5363` / `#838996`
- Accent red (errors only): `#a6021a`

## Typography
- Display/H1: Stack Sans Headline — 72→48→44px, weight 500–600, -0.04em tracking
- H2–H5 + body: Manrope — see doc for scale; body 14–16px, lh 120–150%
- Labels: Manrope 12px semibold

## Layout & style
- Cards: white, 20px radius, soft shadow on gray-100 page bg
- CTAs: olive green, rounded 10–20px, subtle hover
- Generous whitespace; max-width ~1700px; section padding 48–80px
- Mood: calm, premium clinic — warm and trustworthy, not cold/clinical

## Do not
- Use default Expo blue (`#3c87f7`) for primary actions
- Use red for non-error UI
- Ship screens without the shared token palette
